-- Ex-UBS Client Zabczuk Avoids Prison for Hiding Assets From Tax Authority
-- David Voreacos
-- 2010-07-27T17:56:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/ex-ubs-client-zabczuk-avoids-prison-for-hiding-assets-from-tax-authority.html

          
          
             Former UBS AG client Paul Zabczuk,
a Texas businessman, avoided prison today after admitting
earlier he hid assets from U.S. tax authorities.  
